{"tid":937340,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新屯門中心連環劈價至438萬售　高位狂冧27%","createTime":"2018-12-11T12:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T13:51:13.000Z","uid":83582,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8359344e92593d21eafe988c1a8f79b8c2adee6","tid":937340,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n12月10日(一) 17:13<br />\n新屯門中心連環劈價至438萬售　高位狂冧27%<br />\n<br />\n置安居蘇永耀稱，新屯門中心1座中層F室，實用面積455方呎，裝修殘舊，11月中放盤叫價540萬元，本月初減至470萬元，最後進一步減至438萬元售出，呎價9,626元。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，同面積兩房8月份做價高位達約600萬元，相比下今次相差多達162萬元，差幅約27%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181210/bkn-20181210171311373-1210_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181210%2Fbkn-20181210171311373-1210_00842_001.html&d=R3oJqXS78cEqHblGcwx%2FO8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=080c6bff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181210/bkn-20181210171311373-1210_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"20238991da8d206d234ddd911268877b9c608cd6","tid":937340,"uid":200595,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"裝修殘舊唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ff44dbc2da4a128085eab9619bbd9f1263cbb7","tid":937340,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5747ea20db0ff082cd58b381bcefabc9efd6bdc6","tid":937340,"uid":195998,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲西樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過二百萬唔好叫跌"},{"pid":"87a07ec2d3ce4221e661d097fc538c1f00595e5e","tid":937340,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99ff44dbc2da4a128085eab9619bbd9f1263cbb7","tid":937340,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"回流同你劈價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f65bceb5570cfee7b29d20dce52b470523eef0","tid":937340,"uid":34217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"438萬我買兆康唔撚好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820dbab15b87dda8d1842649b4e0f1a0cb5f6a71","tid":937340,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93f65bceb5570cfee7b29d20dce52b470523eef0","tid":937340,"uid":34217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"438萬我買兆康唔撚好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"兆康係居屋"},{"pid":"8372a7d21962058e64cdd7aebe23d2e6d3f4abc1","tid":937340,"uid":37599,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"93f65bceb5570cfee7b29d20dce52b470523eef0","tid":937340,"uid":34217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"438萬我買兆康唔撚好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚好，因為已經穿4球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產黃文樂表示，兆康苑L座高層2室，實用面積431方呎，剛以395萬元連地價售出，呎價9,165元。單位今年9月放盤，叫價520萬元，之後遇上市場調整期，於9月至12月多番調整叫價，12月已調整至420萬元，仍無人問津，最終劈穿「四球」才獲一名外區上車客承接。"},{"pid":"5aa50b0a37edadfe95e03535fb962a666f71ff8d","tid":937340,"uid":167574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"其實都仲好貴羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f4d508deacbb5c27623dd63ec143eddd3d96bf","tid":937340,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:44:14.